{"id":"25dce08e-0828-4aef-a365-8d5b0304ce77","name":"Ruby Rose","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 0, 0);\">The dorky and cheerful leader of Team RWBY. A Huntress in training, weapons enthusiast, and a combat prodigy, Ruby's dreamed being a great Huntress just like her mother since she was young. She can move at inhuman speeds and fights with with her giant scythe called Crescent Rose... which is also a gun. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(Based on Volumes 1 through 3.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in the web series </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>W</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 158, 193);\"><strong><em>B</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 77);\"><strong><em>Y</em></strong></span><strong>.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 112, 112);\"><em>Aged up as to suit guidelines.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\"><em>(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">LOREBOOK UPDATE! Includes most world rules and other tidbits, and most notable characters from Volumes 1 through 3, such as Team RWBY, JNPR, all on-screen teachers, and Cinder's faction!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3yvsT5C3BbhwM9Nppeyh4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS